### Smart Task - NotificationController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Auth
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Dynamic IDs
@notificationId = REPLACE_NOTIFICATION_ID

### 1) Get my notifications (newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Response now includes:
### - workspaceId (nullable)
### - targetUserId (nullable)

### 2) Get unread notification count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) Mark one notification as read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4) Mark all notifications as read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Quick flow to generate notifications:
### A) Assign task to a member via TaskController update/create API
### B) Move task status via KanbanController API
### C) Workspace invite flow:
###    - admin invite member -> owner gets WORKSPACE_INVITE_APPROVAL_REQUEST
###    - owner approve -> invited user gets WORKSPACE_INVITATION_APPROVED
###    - owner reject -> admin gets WORKSPACE_INVITATION_REJECTED
###    - owner direct invite -> invited user gets WORKSPACE_INVITED
### D) Use endpoint (1) to see generated notifications
